    "last_activity_date" : 1375316814,
    "creation_date" : 1375316814,
    "answer_id" : 17983273,
    "question_id" : 16089651,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can also set the global option:</p>\n\n<pre><code>objectMapper.setSerializationInclusion(JsonInclude.Include.NON_NULL);\n</code></pre>\n"
